query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cc cct2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct2 mi) NoMergeJoin(cc cct2 it2 mi mi_idx ci) NoMergeJoin(cc cct2 ci it2 mi mi_idx cct1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it2 mi mi_idx it1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it1 it2 mi mi_idx n) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 ci it1 it2 mi mi_idx mk n k) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(n.name) AS writer,
min(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
from complete_cast AS cc
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Horror',
'Action',
'Sci-Fi',
'Thriller',
'Crime',
'War')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(head writer)',
'(written by)',
'(story)',
'(story editor)')
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'cast'
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres'
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'violence',
'blood',
'gore',
'death',
'female-nudity',
'hospital')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id;
